msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You have beheld true power, as a member of the Sanguine Order.  Power from "
"within, as well as power from beyond.  But at what cost?"
msgstr ""
"「鮮血教団の一員として、現世と異界から溢れ出す真の力を目の当たりにしました。"
