msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"He From Beyond The Veil calls to you, to your brothers and sisters.  And the "
"faithful, those who remain at least, shall bring him into this world."
msgstr ""
"同胞と共に「帳の彼方の神」の呼び声を聞きました。まだ生きている信奉者は、神を"
"この世界に召喚しようとしています。"

